  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/66015113efdf05c3688adb2cc0f167d2.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world of dynamic physics-based entertainment with DADLYMPICS! Unleash laughter as you take on side-splitting dad-worthy challenges alongside friends. Who will emerge as the ultimate dad? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/5c3f60e121abb1ee25ce5ce694a2ae37.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span>Engage in hilarious competitions, conquer quirky tasks, and experience gaming like never before. It's time to showcase your skills and embrace your inner dad in this one-of-a-kind simulator. Are you ready to seize the title of ultimate dad?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by all the dads around the world, Dadlympics aims to pay a homage to all the dads out there with funny and physics-based gameplay. You challenge your friends to different dad activities such as; Mowing the lawn, Packing the car, Grocery shopping and more.. But be on the lookout, there's trouble-makers for dads out there who only want to scrap..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/eba1507c903c3396f2ca4762ede6af6f.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Online multiplayer with up to 6 people</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Character Customization and unlockables</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Wacky Physics-based environments & interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Varied maps with different challenges and strategies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Realistic Dad-noises</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/66015113efdf05c3688adb2cc0f167d2.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world of dynamic physics-based entertainment with DADLYMPICS! Unleash laughter as you take on side-splitting dad-worthy challenges alongside friends. Who will emerge as the ultimate dad? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/5c3f60e121abb1ee25ce5ce694a2ae37.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span>Engage in hilarious competitions, conquer quirky tasks, and experience gaming like never before. It's time to showcase your skills and embrace your inner dad in this one-of-a-kind simulator. Are you ready to seize the title of ultimate dad?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by all the dads around the world, Dadlympics aims to pay a homage to all the dads out there with funny and physics-based gameplay. You challenge your friends to different dad activities such as; Mowing the lawn, Packing the car, Grocery shopping and more.. But be on the lookout, there's trouble-makers for dads out there who only want to scrap..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096760/extras/eba1507c903c3396f2ca4762ede6af6f.avif?t=1763571228\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Online multiplayer with up to 6 people</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Character Customization and unlockables</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Wacky Physics-based environments & interactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Varied maps with different challenges and strategies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹Realistic Dad-noises</p>",
